s to maintain stability in the reward system and support the ongoing liquidity in the ecosystem. By adjusting emissions to match liquidity levels, we aim to ensure a balanced approach that supports both liquidity providers and the overall health of the ecosystem as we move forward.\n \n![1.jpg](ipfs://bafkreiaekwnbtzuo56r6npeisqejb4ue2oudd6hc6hrypusk2ovmnx3ezm)\n    \nApart from the farm mentioned above, any other farms will follow the following APR structure\n\n \n![2.jpg](ipfs://bafkreibn6jkiuedh2ngtn4vdh23v6dub73yru6pgo5rripixe3w7isepfu)\n    \n\n## Technical Specifications\nDemeter farm emissions will be calculated based on the new methodology\n\n## Voting\n#### For: \nImplement new rewards distribution methodology\n#### Against: \nDo not implement the new rewards distribution methodology",
