ap with Saddle which is [currently up for vote in the saddle snapshot. ](https://snapshot.org/#/saddlefinance.eth/proposal/0x3003e0e20359f2bb253705e408ac33de338c2b57fbe38e53ab9f4e15730c1b51)\n\n## Technical Specification\n\nContinue the USDs Saddle farm in its current iteration. 111.111K SPA/day in rewards to be supplied from the Bootstrap Liquidity budget for 30 days.",
